经和区块链的架构绑定在一起。\r\n\r\n有一种理解是，区块链本身就是一种状态机，UTXO 是改变状态的动作。UTXO 怎么是一种模型呢？","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/comments/1059240900/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/comments/1060112683","html_url":"https://github.com/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/19#issuecomment-1060112683","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/19","id":1060112683,"node_id":"IC_kwDOB0TKFM4_MAkr","user":{"login":"smallyunet","id":20765689,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNzY1Njg5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/20765689?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet","html_url":"https://github.com/smallyunet","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-03-07T01:59:46Z","updated_at":"2022-03-07T10:28:56Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"现在越来越喜欢听周杰伦的歌，因为他的歌足够复杂，旋律很多。以前喜欢听李荣浩的一首歌《李白》，现在听起来感觉简单、平庸、无聊。人总是一个不断的从简单到复杂的过程。一开始会喜欢一些简单的东西，觉得这些简单的东西就很好，因为在那个阶段，这些简单的东西就是复杂的，已经足够占用自己处理这些信息的头脑了。\r\n\r\n这对于个人成长来说有什么样的意义呢？可能更多的意义在于，可以通过这样的方式去判断一个人的水平。如果一个人总是喜欢重复地、不断地、乐此不疲地做一些简单的事情，那么就证明他的水平属于简单的阶段。如果一个人无法意识到自己处于那样的阶段，或者不能判断自己做的事情是不是简单的、判断不了一件事情是简单还是复杂，同样说明他处于简单的阶段。","reactions":{"url":"https://a