url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-03-09T07:22:33Z","updated_at":"2022-03-09T07:22:33Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"以前试图基于 “没有第三方依赖包” 的原则设计程序，后来发现不应该重复造轮子，尤其是重复制造的成本很高，以及重复制造的是非常成熟的轮子。\r\n\r\n有时候可能会觉得，如果你不能制造一个东西，那你就不是真的懂。问题在于，懂了又怎么样呢？我们从小就明白 “站在巨人的肩膀上” 的道理，我们不可能把整个世界重新创造一遍，或者把整个人类社会的历程重新体验一遍，以示我们明白它了。\r\n\r\n不过另一方面，又确实不希望做 “缝合怪”，把各种各样的东西拼凑在一起。这里的区别就在于，拿来拼凑的那些东西，不是 “巨人”。所以不是不应该依靠任何东西，而是应该只依靠靠谱的东西。\r\n\r\nBitcoin 的设计其实基于很丰富的已有的技术，但它本身又是很厉害的创新。Bitcoin 的创意绝非偶然，它的作者是很厉害的人。不禁让人好奇，他到底有着怎么样的背景？","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/comments/1062624963/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/comments/1062684447","html_url":"https://github.com/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/19#issuecomment-1062684447","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/smallyunet/hexo-blog/issues/19","id":1062684447,"node_id":"IC_kwDOB0TKFM4_V0cf","user":{"login":"smallyunet","id":20765689,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNzY1Njg5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/20765689?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet","html_url":"https://github.com/smallyunet","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyunet/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smallyun